<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pagamento não aprovado • ZapConnect</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css"
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0D1222;
            --card: #161B30;
            --border: #373E59;
            --text: #FFFFFF;
            --muted: #AAB0D9;
            --primary: #6C64EF;
            --primary-hover: #8B5CF6;
            --danger: #E54848;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #151a3a, var(--bg));
            color: var(--text);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .error-card {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #181f3d, #12172e);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 36px 32px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(108, 100, 239, .35);
            animation: fadeIn .4s ease;
        }

        .icon {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(229, 72, 72, .15);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        .icon i {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .actions {
            margin-top: 26px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-hover));
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(108, 100, 239, .35);
            transition: .2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            filter: brightness(1.15);
        }

        .btn.ghost {
            background: transparent;
            box-shadow: none;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .btn.ghost:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .04);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(14px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* =========================
   ANIMAÇÃO ÍCONE ERRO
========================= */
        .icon {
            animation: errorPop 0.5s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .icon i {
            animation: errorPulse 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes errorPop {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0.6);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            60% {
                transform: scale(1.05);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            80% {
                transform: translateX(-4px);
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1) translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes errorPulse {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }

            50% {
                transform: scale(1.12);
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="error-card">

        <div class="icon">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-xmark"></i>
        </div>

        <h1>Pagamento não aprovado</h1>

        <p>
            Não foi possível confirmar o pagamento.<br>
            Verifique os dados ou tente novamente com outro método.
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/checkout" class="btn">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right"></i>
                Tentar novamente
            </a>

            <a href="/painel" class="btn ghost">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i>
                Voltar ao painel
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>